{"tid":1721400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11.15 旭日行動 請提前出門時間","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T00:37:13.000Z","uid":39859,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"62cf1ceb34365ece19b76e18447767a13377d752","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"知道大家依幾日好攰<br />\n但今日太遲行動8點好多港豬都返晒工 <br />\n<br />\n我公司群組依幾日 <br />\n某啲上咗年紀係無報過自己遲到 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">係連續4日既三罷行動都無影響過佢地遲一分鐘！</span><br />\n證明佢地係6-7點已經好早起身返到公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHVeWSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHVeWSb.jpg&h=d3fe1a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11.15 旭日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n可以預計聽日大家會面對某程度上既<span style=\"color: red;\">沖擊</span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: orange;\">請唔好再blakcbloc</span>係屋企行出去須要時先變身<br />\n2. 鐵方面<span style=\"color: pink;\">唔好再用肉身擋 </span><br />\n製作番各種<span style=\"color: gold;\">小道具</span>  道門就已經閂唔到<br />\n3. 唔好<span style=\"color: red;\">單獨行動</span><br />\n4. 可以既話 大家今晚盡量唔好太夜<br />\n以確保第2朝早可以出黎活動 <br />\n一黎成效大D 二黎各位手足都<span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span><br />\n5. 今朝各位熱愛番工既市民大清早5點半就開始出門口<br />\n大家自行考慮要唔要將活動提早到6點<br />\n地點 有兩個方向 <br />\n一係列車正中間同人一齊迫 <br />\n一係頭尾 係車門做左手腳之後行開<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">安全第一</span><br />\n<br />\n最後 我只係希望各位可以平平安安<br />\n咩都唔夠條命咁重要[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n11.15 旭日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db48de256aca5b4f7f2637ff0e0763566baaabb3","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"和理非想塞地鐵又淆底既入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1711917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1711917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c59272a70732f5e5669674d61d00773183e8e57","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"[11.15突發，推上熱門]屋企張床要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cac0456149ff5742ebe17a3c219e2e99419be244","tid":1721400,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e51f5832c7623db307a736335c423a01a1b8e79","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"[旭日行動］聽日改早到6:00搭地鐵好唔好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n準時見大家！<br />\n大家要知道集合時間永遠等得嚟都拖到唔知幾點 <br />\n全民早啲返工搭地鐵！<br />\n我要出門返工！！"},{"pid":"aa8fc23767be36cd6f380621a105d5dc3c6f095a","tid":1721400,"uid":3865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"［旭日行動］唔好太依賴塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4629809f0e774f3b8351bc834404771634c68e9","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8fc23767be36cd6f380621a105d5dc3c6f095a","tid":1721400,"uid":3865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"［旭日行動］唔好太依賴塞鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"Push!!<br />\n<br />\n分散晒唔夠人 只會一直推遲<br />\n<br />\nQuote 返post<br />\n<br />\n我知你地玩攝門解鎖新成就好開心<br />\n但好多人都係靠巴士小巴番工<br />\n要諗下主要公路可以點玩<br />\n<br />\nEg <br />\n龍翔道 &mdash; 九龍灣觀塘<br />\n紅隧 西隧 東區走廊 &mdash; 港島<br />\n彌敦道 &mdash; 旺角尖沙咀<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵既唔該集中令人去唔到<br />\n旺角觀塘中環<br />\n<br />\n下面大家討論下點玩會最大效益<br />\n<br />\n荔景 &mdash; 東涌線往香港<br />\n美孚 &mdash; 大西北轉紅色線<br />\n太子<br />\n九龍塘 &mdash; 九龍灣至觀塘<br />\n尖沙咀 &mdash; 往港島<br />\n北角 &mdash; 往中環<br />\n<br />\n聽日我唔要見到有人番到工呀！"},{"pid":"d9fe33178196864feaf621986c80da349e13786b","tid":1721400,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f3a73666401dcec672595b0b9987a312c8e953f","tid":1721400,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"(一句激嬲藍絲港奴) 公司都默許我地遲到，點解仲要咁蠢要咁早番？lunch後先番唔好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb426e75489df1908c6aade4fc33f27779f3bcd2","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d4ec706116302593f85932b705c3a29bd11381","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"445d578fdd50122bf95962de8ef9bfb01fdfe2da","tid":1721400,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55454b5b4a64dde9fe6e4aca8d26d42617363c9e","tid":1721400,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"記得廢鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6256d2701088a16a0d3d2e4ae347559f775db7","tid":1721400,"uid":39859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06ae11be0cb46a15248ccad0e6c0b9b7a8d7b6c9","tid":1721400,"uid":150625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"一定要廢鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=